race.comment: FILLY GAGA (2) missed the placings two runs back then settled well back last start when 3 lengths away in eighth over 274m at Retama Park. Nicely placed to get the prize. KVN CORRE (1) has switched yards since scoring by 0.8 lengths at Retama Park over 402m on August 7. Rates highly and makes plenty of appeal. BV BIG BUX (4) started at $5.40 last time and ran below expectations, finishing fifth and beaten 1.4 lengths at Delta Downs (Dirt) over 274m. Meeting a tougher field but on his best form he is capable of testing his rivals. JESS JJ WATT AW (6) was unplaced two runs back then again missed the frame last start over 366m at Gillespie County Fairground, beaten 5 lengths into eighth. Likely improver with strong top-three prospects.
